{"id": 2033, "genre": 1000, "title": "有关看病、健康管理的那些 App，你有啥想吐槽的？", "description": "生病看病已经够难受了，还要被它们再添点堵。（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 3569, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171124154358lV7jvDFtLzBJaY0W.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-11-27T17:00:22Z", "questions": [{"id": 3341, "title": "有关看病、健康管理的那些 App，你有啥想吐槽的？", "content": "关于健康管理、看病的那些 App，哪些你想吐槽？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 250881, "content": "挂号功能的信息都不是很全，一个平台挂不到的号在另一个又可以挂了", "image": "img/option/option/20171127151237edjn3l0sHt2BFZxk.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 251184, "content": "有用的信息不足，不知道该怎样选科室和医生", "image": "img/option/option/20171127165756ajnoUxJzAf1ctdX3.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 250885, "content": "医院官方做的智慧医疗等 App，功能和信息常有滞后", "image": "img/option/option/20171127151430rHuE1idyWt7YI8N2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 251175, "content": "功能过多，挂号就医、健康管理、药品查询挤在一起，经常找不到要用的东西", "image": "img/option/option/20171127162424s14flC9aruE7hiPK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 250883, "content": "医学问答板块大部分是针对疾病的问题，一些生活中常见的健康问题还是找不到答案", "image": "img/option/option/20171127165445pSsFJ8YxgP6tyBEk.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 251039, "content": "症状查询中的信息复杂，有关本疾病添油加醋的问答还会让人恐慌", "image": "img/option/option/201711271658150hCwo8X7vAUF4rZf.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 250884, "content": "在线问诊的结果不尽如人意，好医生很多没空参与这个", "image": "img/option/option/20171127164243M9A4UthP1cr06YEy.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 250893, "content": "做电商，但我只是想记录饮食健康数据，你整天给我推荐美白产品干嘛？", "image": "img/option/option/20171127165413K2FDd6qypzeSPRlY.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}